      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge rv">
      <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      Gas Safe Registered
    </div>
    <h1 class="rv rv-d1">Boiler repair in Leeds you can rely&nbsp;on</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub rv rv-d2">15 years keeping Leeds warm. Emergency repairs, annual servicing, and full installations — available 24/7 with parts on the van.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns rv rv-d3">
      <a href="tel:07515314131" class="btn btn-primary">
        <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 01-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 014.11 2h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg>
        Call Now
      </a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn btn-outline">View Services</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-trust rv rv-d3">
      <span class="hero-trust-item">
        <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
        Gas Safe Registered
      </span>
      <span class="hero-trust-item">
        <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
        24/7 Emergency
      </span>
      <span class="hero-trust-item">
        <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
        5-Star Google Reviews
      </span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div class="stats rv">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">15+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Years Experience</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">90%</div>
      <div class="stat-label">First Visit Fix</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">24/7</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Availability</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">5.0</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Google Rating</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="services" id="services">
    <div class="section-label rv">Services</div>
    <h2 class="section-title rv rv-d1">Everything your boiler needs</h2>
    <p class="section-desc rv rv-d2">From emergency breakdowns to annual servicing. Gas Safe registered and available around the clock across Leeds and West Yorkshire.</p>

    <div class="services-list">
      <div class="svc rv">
        <div class="svc-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Boiler Repair</h3>
        <p>Quick diagnosis and repair for any boiler type, at competitive prices. Most jobs completed on the first visit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc rv rv-d1">
        <div class="svc-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Boiler Servicing</h3>
        <p>Annual servicing to keep your boiler running smoothly, avoid breakdowns and reduce energy costs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc rv rv-d2">
        <div class="svc-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a4 4 0 00-8 0v2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>New Installations</h3>
        <p>Full boiler and heating installations, done efficiently and at a time that suits you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc rv">
        <div class="svc-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83M2 12h4M18 12h4M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Gas Appliances</h3>
        <p>Cooker installations, gas hob connections, and appliance safety checks by Gas Safe engineers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc rv rv-d1">
        <div class="svc-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8l-6-6z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6M16 13H8M16 17H8M10 9H8"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Gas Safety Certificates</h3>
        <p>Landlord and homeowner gas safety inspections. Ensuring your property meets all legal requirements.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc rv rv-d2">
        <div class="svc-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
